rtkit|-----handy-ruler------------------------------------------------------|
rtkit: rtkit (Realtime Policy and Watchdog Daemon)
rtkit:
rtkit: RealtimeKit is a D-Bus system service that changes the scheduling
rtkit: policy of user processes/threads to SCHED_RR (i.e. realtime scheduling
rtkit: mode) on request. It is intended to be used as a secure mechanism to
rtkit: allow real-time scheduling to be used by normal user processes.
rtkit:
rtkit: http://git.0pointer.de/?p=rtkit.git
rtkit:
